title: CCleaner 5.12.5431 AIO + Key & DLL
description:
CCleaner 5.12.5431 Free, Professional, Business and Technical Edition


If you have CCleaner already installed on your PC, than let the program automatically update and download only the key to register. Other wise you must download the installer and the key.

Your computer is not only at risk from being infected by malicious software, residues left after uninstalling applications and so-called junk files can significantly reduce oerformance. However perodic scans and cleaning can keep your PC in good shape. One of the applications that can aid in this situation is CCleaner, equipped with all tools needed to scrub every bit of your computer.

We've also optimized internal architecture so CCleaner will launch quicker than ever before.



Changelog: v5.12.5431  (Release date: 24 November 2015) 


- Improved Firefox 42 Cache cleaning. 
- Improved Google Chrome Download History cleaning. 
- Improved Skip UAC on Windows 10. 
- Improved detection and cleaning of portable browsers. 
- Optimized cleaning rules loading routine. 
- Improved localization and language support. 
- Minor GUI Improvements. 
- Minor bug fixes.



System Requirements: Windows 10, 8.1, 8, 7, Vista and XP. Including both 32-bit and 64-bit versions. 



NOTE: Standard CCleaner version (includes optional install of Google products)
